	.string "{COLOR BLUE}EA{COLOR DARK_GRAY}: This world was once at peace, but\p"
	.string "{COLOR GREEN}TIAMET{COLOR DARK_GRAY}, goddess of chaos,\n"
	.string "has plunged us into war.\p"
	.string "She created these creatures to\n"
	.string "unleash her fury against the gods.$"

gText_Birch_Pokemon::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}EA{COLOR DARK_GRAY}: These creatures, forged in chaos\n"
	.string "by {COLOR GREEN}TIAMET{COLOR DARK_GRAY}, now serve as our only means\n"
	.string "to resist her wrath.\p"
	.string "With my magic, you will command them.\p$"

gText_Birch_WarHistory::
	.string "{COLOR BLUE}EA{COLOR DARK_GRAY}: Long ago, the gods lived in balance,\n"
	.string "each ruling their own domain.\p"
	.string "But {COLOR GREEN}TIAMET{COLOR DARK_GRAY}'s thirst for domination grew,\n"
	.string "leading to this war.\p"
	.string "Now, the gods are scattered, and her\n"
	.string "creations wreak havoc across the world.\p$"

